_sText: Aim_ag_radical ----------- 12 players or less (preferred) Description: A simple skill map set within a small arena with objects placed tactically forcing you to use skill to eliminate your enemies. This is a texture map. I made this map to a design from a friend (radical). Objective: Use the objects and environment to beat your enemies in gunfights. Pure skill will save you from getting that one headshot you didn't deserve.
